    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents an effect that can be added to a <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Mob" kindref="compound">Mob</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>An effect is an immutable description of an effect type together with a duration, amplifier and a set of display options. Applying it to a <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Mob" kindref="compound">Mob</ref> (e.g. via <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Mob_1a2836f61e2312723e336e43e41f0604f3" kindref="member">Mob::addEffect</ref>) installs the effect; querying a <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Mob" kindref="compound">Mob</ref>&apos;s active effects yields <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Effect" kindref="compound">Effect</ref> values describing what is currently in force. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
